 The 13th century castle in the Dordogne , France has been placed on the market for less than half the price of a flat in London .
The 14-bedroom home also features 14 bathrooms and its own suit of armour - as well as 46 hectares of land .
The castle dates from the 13thth and was refurbished in the 19th century .
the castle is only 15 minutes from Bordeaux .